hands_on_practices.solution:
我们有一个反对称联络和常数挠率
$$T^k_{ij}=\Gamma^k_{ij}-\Gamma^k_{ji},\qquad \Gamma^k_{ij}=-\Gamma^k_{ji}$$ 
所以
$$\Gamma^k_{ij}=\tfrac12T^k_{ij}.$$ 
唯一的非零挠率分量是
$$T^1_{12}=c_1,\quad T^2_{12}=c_2,$$ 
因此
$$\Gamma^1_{12}=\tfrac{c_1}{2},\;
\Gamma^2_{12}=\tfrac{c_2}{2},\;
\Gamma^k_{21}=-\Gamma^k_{12}.$$ 

曲率为
$$R^l_{kij}
=\partial_i\Gamma^l_{kj}-\partial_j\Gamma^l_{ki}
+\Gamma^m_{ki}\Gamma^l_{mj}-\Gamma^m_{kj}\Gamma^l_{mi}
=\Gamma^m_{ki}\Gamma^l_{mj}-\Gamma^m_{kj}\Gamma^l_{mi},$$ 
因为 $\Gamma^l_{kj}$ 是常数。里奇张量是
$$R_{jk}=R^i_{jik},\qquad R=g^{jk}R_{jk}=R_{11}+R_{22},$$ 
其中
$$R_{11}=R^2_{121},\quad R_{22}=R^1_{212}.$$ 
计算
$$R^2_{121}
=\Gamma^m_{12}\Gamma^2_{m1}
=(\Gamma^2_{12})(\Gamma^2_{21})
=\frac{c_2}{2}\Bigl(-\frac{c_2}{2}\Bigr)
=-\frac{c_2^2}{4},$$ 
$$R^1_{212}
=\Gamma^m_{21}\Gamma^1_{m2}
=(\Gamma^1_{21})(\Gamma^1_{12})
=\Bigl(-\frac{c_1}{2}\Bigr)\frac{c_1}{2}
=-\frac{c_1^2}{4}.$$ 
因此里奇标量是
$$R=R_{11}+R_{22}
=-\frac{c_2^2}{4}-\frac{c_1^2}{4}
=-\frac{c_1^2+c_2^2}{4}.$$
